{"tid":2183950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店唔只排除異己，仲公然預告違反勞工法例","createTime":"2020-09-01T08:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:58:47.000Z","uid":67412,"like":11,"dislike":229,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"cae05669bf2e8c4e5deaeef7d3910997a25d557f","tid":2183950,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"所謂不分化，原來唔只踩同路人組織，仲要預告自己無人性&amp;公然犯勞工法例<br />\n<br />\n係進入千字文前首先講聲對唔住，香港仲有好多大事需要連登師兄師姐關注！<br />\n<br />\n但打著黃店號，排除異己，公然欺壓基層，咁樣的黃圈健康咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果講有乜事私下解決唔好上連登攪大件事，咁仲要連登做乜？以後藍屍做仆街嘢，報警啦！有警察嫁嘛！黑囧仆街？投訴科囉！香港仲有司法機關嘛.....<br />\n<br />\n進入正題，首先，唔好話我老屈，俾左cap 圖大家睇先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDFkvxM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDFkvxM.jpg&h=7629a555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲政治正確point就唔講啦，想大家留意第三，第四，同後面段抽水文<br />\n<br />\n第三:一定要和諧！創建文明工作環境<br />\n當然，企業唔係公民社會，無可能民主化同由下而上，但最小要尊重員工的意見同感受！老闆唔好以為自己出錢出技術就一統天下，同你打生打死的係你前線！<br />\n你無犯法，但犯左企業管理其中一個大忌囉！<br />\n而且身為黃店，鼓勵呢種虛假的和諧，同暴政有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n第四:一定要勤奮！唔容許遲到早退射波！<br />\n首先，一定要勤奮就無錯，但...<br />\n唔容許遲到早退都唔算錯，規律對一間公司係好重要，但你合約一定要寫得好清楚！塞車呢？天災人禍呢？社會運動呢？係咪一秒都唔遲得先？<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔容許射波</span><br />\n呢個point最仆街！唔講紅白二事社會運動！唔俾人病嫁？你仲要係一間食店！係咪叫人中左武肺都一定要返工呀？仲有，病假係勞工法例嚟嫁！<br />\n<br />\n有關抽勞工__水部份，其實一隻手指指人四隻手指指自己！你學中共講嘢咪即係同意中共唔俾國際社會救援香港囉！咁都仲有資格叫自己黃店？<br />\n<br />\n總結，大家可唔可以反思下乜嘢係黃店！係一句反暴政就得，定係有公義有良心？<br />\n當然，係香港，從事飲食非常困難，而香港真係好多公司對員工好仆街，現金糧唔供強姦金無保險假自僱等....<br />\n但，係咪多人咁做就啱先？<br />\n作為黃店，如果你係對僱員公平友善而導致成本增加，而你的服務同出品值得支持的話，係有權用呢個selling point加價！就好似[公平貿易貨品]一樣，你的良知都可以係一個賣點！<br />\n但做生意就係要量入為出，你俾唔到合理的人事成本就唔好請人！等同你俾唔到貨錢租金就無貨無店一樣！小本經營唔係欺壓基層的借口！<br />\n<br />\n最後，都仲係嗰句<br />\n黃店就係同路人要不分化<br />\n勞工組就要鬥死鬥臭<br />\n你們的不分化真係分化到令人作嘔！"},{"pid":"9522016ee8a39d3c1868199463849de1b659ab5a","tid":2183950,"uid":48083,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"睇完<br />\n樓主完全係夾硬揾野屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c50633520e25665a1e7a774f1333f56cdef05b","tid":2183950,"uid":41873,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e9770f65c6a84709189c35045d990b7a76eab0","tid":2183950,"uid":119895,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"手足揾同路人既勞工組織都唔撚得？<br />\n佢請手足定請奴隸？<br />\n炒人冇問題，唔該跟番勞工法例回水"},{"pid":"9487b77bf357f6a863e5bf42663fcd885ce5ca83","tid":2183950,"uid":13867,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"樓主完全係夾硬揾野屌"},{"pid":"490c4410691cbbc3fc0f9d361451f501c43aba55","tid":2183950,"uid":143343,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82446e78e7270c9af6c92c6f34660f6d30edefbd","tid":2183950,"uid":203397,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"去黃店做HR好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以惡撚過黑狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然時不時比太上皇屌下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一諗到可以打柒啲工友就爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">黃店見字請HR</span>"},{"pid":"9f4a62d1881426ec8eaa43c15472c57c08add952","tid":2183950,"uid":159736,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"睇完, 唔覺有問題  樓主太得閒?"},{"pid":"86f455fd1e6e5307c1722023935a6988efc1a1b1","tid":2183950,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"病假係勞工法例<br />\n要睇你幾多日<br />\n少過四日真係出俾你係人情唔出俾你係道理<br />\n有種就下下長期病患咁款<br />\n不過都係要儲返黎"},{"pid":"8636bdfceb87bb4e1818cedcd58bcea13173510d","tid":2183950,"uid":236878,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:14:50.000Z","msg":"我睇完最尾果段覺得係曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保持3秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f773f645171fc4c9aef6caf036eb19e967e01df4","tid":2183950,"uid":266591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"樓主你成功左喇 我同黃店割左 去親中喇!"},{"pid":"c9e3e99f7e3cf96495df143da24161b736d4e6f4","tid":2183950,"uid":203397,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8636bdfceb87bb4e1818cedcd58bcea13173510d","tid":2183950,"uid":236878,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:14:50.000Z","msg":"我睇完最尾果段覺得係曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保持3秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"似廣告，間野有撚人識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8d8e5fbf70a7bbda4c41e71a0fd5ca52420798","tid":2183950,"uid":172948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"第四點真係你冇野搵黎講<br />\n射波喎<br />\n如果你紅事白事一早講定仲叫射波咩?<br />\n如果你病係咪要提早通知呢?<br />\n射波即係冇通知情況下缺勤"},{"pid":"30e577f4211a30287adc945da62a344c389f88eb","tid":2183950,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"你可以對自己冇要求 冇責任心<br />\n但係遲到射波俾人屌嗰時冇得你唔認<br />\n<br />\n利申日日遲半個鐘返工準時走"},{"pid":"534a4b4f678669e61f06e49068fbcc8d061457a8","tid":2183950,"uid":21170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"樓主條傻鳩連射波定義都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺香港返過工未？"},{"pid":"ab07aa2a4e36ae73e347d0ba7f164c8105855d59","tid":2183950,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪新移民?? 射波都未知點解"},{"pid":"5f9dd00152fe76d167f58c0abe0ab1e351840f8a","tid":2183950,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"我唔一個一個回<br />\n有講錯歡迎屌<br />\n(我認我好玻璃心但上得連登預左係心理自殺)<br />\n我係咪藍屍？當然係啦！藍到黑！<br />\n你地呢種黃法我真係高攀唔起！<br />\n但我係一個每月得萬幾人工的廢老！<br />\n無資格開店！<br />\n請善用起底功能！"},{"pid":"5b0aece1f991ffd1d79f9b2c989b9a1166cea7ee","tid":2183950,"uid":263200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺有咩問題，為屌而屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e72fd45bed7a2a19d52c027c59f26d8fa0a92c7","tid":2183950,"uid":66221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"「射波」一詞意指「事先未經申請就自行放假、唔返工」<br />\n樓豬其實係咪將無故缺席同請病假撈亂咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a5b2df5a3d84e7bc12cf1a6f5916c3722aee20","tid":2183950,"uid":138713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"a6ce4b716f6397f35a9450d35e66ca03413fc5ff","tid":2183950,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"似係你冇野搵野黎講喎"},{"pid":"a65fdbbc127fca92e9378b49203602a469db4a4b","tid":2183950,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"雞蛋裏挑骨頭，拉"},{"pid":"bed37a7ee436e2de8db636d7b8ea8056aa93ca4d","tid":2183950,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1e72fd45bed7a2a19d52c027c59f26d8fa0a92c7","tid":2183950,"uid":66221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"「射波」一詞意指「事先未經申請就自行放假、唔返工」<br />\n樓豬其實係咪將無故缺席同請病假撈亂咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces